        This stores all the timestamps related to this node. All the timestamps are coming from the front end.

      • parentId

        private java.lang.String parentId
        This is the parent id of the NoteNode it is associated with. It is default to "root" for NoteNode types NoteNode and ListNode. NodeType ListItem and Attachment will have parent id of either NoteNode or ListNode.
